928
01:06:57,738 --> 01:06:59,168
<i>You can't go like this.</i>

929
01:06:59,238 --> 01:07:01,108
<i>I found the footage
of your brother's accident.</i>

930
01:07:01,178 --> 01:07:04,148
<i>Are you sure Hong Dae-young is
the guy in the footage?</i>

931
01:07:04,278 --> 01:07:06,678
<i>Did you have fun lying to me?</i>

932
01:07:06,748 --> 01:07:09,548
<i>If you hid it from me,
