933
01:07:09,618 --> 01:07:11,218
<i>Why did you come back to me?</i>

934
01:07:11,288 --> 01:07:13,788
<i>Whenever you were by my side,</i>

935
01:07:13,988 --> 01:07:16,018
<i>do you know what went through my head?</i>

936
01:07:16,818 --> 01:07:17,988
<i>"I miss you,"</i>

937
01:07:18,588 --> 01:07:19,858
<i>"Hong Dae-young."</i>

